## CRITICAL: PyTorch CPU-only install

Always install PyTorch with the CPU wheel URL.
The default pip install downloads a 2 GB CUDA build unnecessarily.

```bash
pip install torch==2.3.0 --index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

