# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECTION 8 — API ENDPOINTS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

All endpoints require JWT except /api/auth/login and /api/health*.
Tenant ID: extracted from JWT ONLY — never from request.

```
POST   /api/auth/login              public   — JWT access + httpOnly refresh
POST   /api/auth/refresh            public   — new access token
POST   /api/auth/logout             any      — invalidate refresh token
GET    /api/auth/me                 any      — current user + role

POST   /api/query                   any      — full JSON response
GET    /api/query/stream            any      — SSE streaming
GET    /api/query/history           any      — paginated history

POST   /api/documents/upload        auditor+ — triggers Celery task
GET    /api/documents               any      — RBAC-filtered list
GET    /api/documents/{id}          any      — metadata (RBAC-checked)
GET    /api/documents/{id}/status   any      — ingestion task status
DELETE /api/documents/{id}          auditor+ — soft delete

GET    /api/admin/users             admin    — list tenant users
POST   /api/admin/users             admin    — create user
PUT    /api/admin/users/{id}        admin    — update role/status
DELETE /api/admin/users/{id}        admin    — deactivate user
GET    /api/admin/audit-log         admin    — paginated, filterable
GET    /api/admin/stats             admin    — aggregated usage metrics
GET    /api/admin/queue             admin    — current LLM queue status

GET    /api/health                  public   — liveness (200 if running)
GET    /api/health/ready            public   — readiness (checks all deps)
```

---

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECTION 9 — SECURITY IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Generate code that implements ALL of the following:

- [ ] JWT access tokens: 60-minute expiry
- [ ] Refresh tokens: 7-day expiry, stored in httpOnly cookie (NOT localStorage)
- [ ] RBAC dependency applied on every protected route
- [ ] Tenant ID from JWT only — never from request
- [ ] Document ACL checked in semantic.py BEFORE chunk retrieval
- [ ] Prompt sanitisation: null bytes, control chars, injection patterns
- [ ] Chunks wrapped in <DOC> tags in all prompts
- [ ] System prompt forbids treating DOC content as instructions
- [ ] Audit log written for: login, query, upload, delete, admin actions
- [ ] Audit log: no UPDATE or DELETE for app DB user (REVOKE at DB level)
- [ ] Ollama URL hardcoded to 127.0.0.1 — NOT configurable via env
- [ ] Rate limiting: 60 req/min per user on /api/query* (slowapi)
- [ ] File upload: validate MIME type AND magic bytes (not just extension)
- [ ] Max file upload size: 50 MB
- [ ] CORS: only FRONTEND_URL from env — no wildcard origins
- [ ] Ollama port bound to 127.0.0.1 in docker-compose (not 0.0.0.0)
- [ ] Redis port bound to 127.0.0.1 in docker-compose
- [ ] DB port NOT exposed in docker-compose (internal network only)
- [ ] Row hash on every audit_log entry: SHA-256(all field values)

